            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Asalamu alaikum wr wb\nAs a parent of student studying in Al fajr international school Alhamdhulillah all praise to allah that we have made a best decision of joining this school. This is best school for studying both academic and islamic under one roof.....jazakallahu khairan for the efforts taken by the teachers,co workers and management...keep up the work and we are awaiting for further encouraging activities too....",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
