          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school has made a well organized function with full support from the management and school teachers.\n\nThey have concentrated on micro details and made this funtion a very successful event.\n\nMay Allah give them more success towards the path of education for both in this world and aahira",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Al-Fajr International School - Maraimalai Nagar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Mohamed Izaan"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-12-17",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My son is studying here for the past 5 years and I am very happy with all the aspects of the school. The student teacher ratio is great. It not only focuses on academics but the whole personality of the child. There are many extra curricular activities, islamic, athletic and other, and they make sure that all the children come forward, making sure nobody is left behind. This really brings out the best in children.\nThe teachers and ustads are very dedicated and go to great lengths to make sure that every child gets good attention.\nThe school strives in overall development of the children, brings out their confidence, but also teaches them to be humble.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Al-Fajr International School - Maraimalai Nagar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Kamran Akmal"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-01-10",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a Student of Al-Fajr International School for a decade, I would say Al fajr is a very good school for a few reasons.\n1. It's environment-the students are very respectful to everyone. Kind and humble.\n2. There are very well qualified teachers.\n3. The most important one- the student to teacher ratio is very less which enables Teachers to focus on each and every students.\n4. During Covid Classes were conducted online.\n5.  Knowledgeable field trips are conducted for students to learn practically.\n6.Students are taken to turfs and badminton courts during the Playing session. Improvement needed in this sector.\n7. A little bit more improvement needed on extracurricular activities.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        }
      ]
